Well done.

292
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:39,120
What a good son.

293
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:42,240
It seems

294
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:44,680
the fight between you and me

295
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:47,320
is about to start.

296
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:50,600
What a pity.

297
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:50,400
Where

298
00:15:50,400 --> 00:15:51,240
have you been?

299
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:54,920
Do I have to report to you?

300
00:15:57,040 --> 00:15:57,960
You're injured. Stay away from me.

301
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:02,480
Get ready.

302
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:04,560
I'll have someone take you away tomorrow morning.

303
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:06,240
What do you mean?

304
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:07,160
I said...

305
00:16:08,520 --> 00:16:09,840
I told you to get out.

306
00:16:14,760 --> 00:16:15,760
You finally came to your senses.

307
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,040
Mr. Fu

308
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:20,040
is tired of playing.

309
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:20,840
Yes.

310
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:21,760
I'm tired of it.

311
00:16:22,760 --> 00:16:24,160
Since you don't care about me,

312
00:16:24,640 --> 00:16:26,800
it's pointless to keep a hostage by my side.

313
00:16:27,160 --> 00:16:28,320
What happened to you?

314
00:16:28,320 --> 00:16:29,160
It's none of your business.

315
00:16:29,160 --> 00:16:29,840
Pang Jingfu.

316
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:30,240
Are you...

317
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,400
I told you to get lost!

318
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:33,120
Do you understand?

319
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:34,560
Stay as far away from me as possible.

320
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:37,480
I'm sick of seeing your face right now.

321
00:16:43,680 --> 00:16:44,360
Where are you hurt?

322
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:45,000
Let me see.

323
00:16:45,520 --> 00:16:46,120
What?

324
00:16:46,880 --> 00:16:48,360
Now you've learned to care?

325
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:49,560
Tian Yan,

326
00:16:50,520 --> 00:16:52,160
don't you wish I were dead?

327
00:16:52,760 --> 00:16:54,280
Take off your clothes and let me see the wound.

328
00:16:58,040 --> 00:16:59,440
Now you want me?

329
00:17:01,800 --> 00:17:03,200
No wonder you're waiting here.

330
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:07,840
I was interested in you before

331
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:10,880
because you were good at pretending

332
00:17:12,240 --> 00:17:13,280
and seducing.

333
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:16,520
But now I'm sick of you.

334
00:17:25,160 --> 00:17:26,640
I'll say it one last time,

335
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:28,080
get lost!

336
00:17:29,360 --> 00:17:30,600
Before I change my mind

337
00:17:30,600 --> 00:17:32,320
and throw you and your grandma into the sea.

338
00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:44,720
Tian Yan,

339
00:17:46,040 --> 00:17:46,760
go.

340
00:17:48,040 --> 00:17:49,080
Don't come back.

341
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:51,800
It's too dangerous around me.

342
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:55,320
I'd rather you didn't love me.

343
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:58,320
I just want you to be alive.
